      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major project for a dedicated mechanic. The engine currently runs very roughly and has significant oil leaks, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping and difficulty engaging gears. Cosmetically, the body has several large dents and areas of heavy rust, and the interior shows extreme wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing is advised as it is not reliable for long-distance driving.",
